name: Screaming Parrots of Pasadena
description: These things sound like several high pitch alarms going off at once. IT was Los Angeles, Pasadena to be exact. They say there's over 1000 wild parrots there alone. The correct term for a group of parrots is a "pandemonium".  There will be 100 editions to start, for free, then  I will burn the pandemonium. As long as they live forever on the blockchain.
